@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "CV Parser" as CVParser
participant "Screening Question Validator" as ScreeningQuestionValidator
participant "Cosine Similarity Calculator" as CosineSimilarityCalculator
participant "Jaccard Similarity Calculator" as JaccardSimilarityCalculator
participant "Rating Generator" as RatingGenerator
participant "CV Comparison Module" as CVComparisonModule
participant "ChatGPT Validator" as ChatGPTValidator
participant "Submit CV Module" as SubmitCVModule
participant "View and Edit CV Module" as ViewandEditCVModule
participant "Answer Screening Questions Module" as AnswerScreeningQuestionsModule
participant "Get Rating for CV Module" as GetRatingforCVModule
SubmitCVModule -> CVParser : Parse and extract key information from the applicant's CV
CVParser -> CVComparisonModule : Compare CV information with job requirements and generate a ranking
CVComparisonModule -> RatingGenerator : Generate a percentage-based result representing the applicant's overall suitability for the role
CVComparisonModule -> GetRatingforCVModule : Provide applicants with a rating for their submitted CV
SubmitCVModule ->> ViewandEditCVModule : Enable applicants to view and edit their parsed CV
ViewandEditCVModule ->> SubmitCVModule : Allow applicants to submit their CVs for parsing and analysis
AnswerScreeningQuestionsModule -> ScreeningQuestionValidator : Verify and grade applicant responses against an expert-generated model
ScreeningQuestionValidator -> RatingGenerator : Generate a percentage-based result representing the applicant's overall suitability for the role
SubmitCVModule -> ChatGPTValidator : Validate and score applicant responses using ChatGPT
ChatGPTValidator -> RatingGenerator : Generate a percentage-based result representing the applicant's overall suitability for the role
SubmitCVModule -> CosineSimilarityCalculator : Assess the alignment between CV information and job requirements using cosine similarity
CosineSimilarityCalculator -> CVComparisonModule : Compare CV information with job requirements and generate a ranking
SubmitCVModule -> JaccardSimilarityCalculator : Assess the alignment between CV information and job requirements using Jaccard similarity
JaccardSimilarityCalculator -> CVComparisonModule : Compare CV information with job requirements and generate a ranking
AnswerScreeningQuestionsModule -> ChatGPTValidator : Validate and score applicant responses using ChatGPT
ChatGPTValidator -> RatingGenerator : Generate a percentage-based result representing the applicant's overall suitability for the role
@enduml